Vue 3 patterns
- Use `<script setup>` with `ref/reactive/computed`.
- Prefer `defineProps`, `defineEmits`, `defineModel`.
- Provide/inject only for true cross-tree deps; otherwise composables.
- Template-first rendering; computed > methods for derived state.
